<configs>

<!-- 
In MickkPewPew mod originally has all entities spawn in the Wasteland. In merging with the custom biome groups that enZombies uses below, the MickkPewPew entities will spawn in the following biomes, which better matches their looks. 

BIOME		ENTITY					
forest		zombieLumberjackBossSnow
desert		zombieSpiderRadiatedBoss
snow		zombieLumberjackBossSnow
burnt		animalZombieDogBoss, zombieBurntFeralBoss, PyromaniacBoss, Lucifer
wasteland	WraithRB, zombieMutatedRadiatedBoss, animalZombieVultureRadiatedBossSnow, animalZombieVultureRadiatedBoss, animalMountainLionBossSnow, animalDireWolfBossSnow, BalorTheMalevolentWorldBoss

BalorTheMalevolentWorldBoss has low spawn probability for automatic spawn due to its OP stats. The main intention is for the server admin to manually spawn during battle events.
-->


<!-- ********************************** -->
<!-- ********** FOREST BIOME ********** -->
<!-- ********************************** -->	

<!-- DAY SPAWNING OUTSIDE WILDERNESS -->
<append xpath="/entitygroups/entitygroup[@name='PineforestZombiesDay']">
	<entity name="zombieLumberjackBossSnow" prob="0.10"/>
</append>

<!-- DAY SPAWNING COMMERCIAL / INDUSTRIAL -->
<append xpath="/entitygroups/entitygroup[@name='PineforestZombiesDayCity']">
	<entity name="zombieLumberjackBossSnow" prob="0.05"/>
</append>

<!-- NIGHT SPAWNING OUTSIDE WILDERNESS -->
<append xpath="/entitygroups/entitygroup[@name='PineforestZombiesNight']">
	<entity name="zombieLumberjackBossSnow" prob="0.10"/>
</append>

<!-- NIGHT SPAWNING COMMERCIAL / INDUSTRIAL -->
<append xpath="/entitygroups/entitygroup[@name='PineforestZombiesNightCity']">
	<entity name="zombieLumberjackBossSnow" prob="0.05"/>
</append>




